/*
Developed a Page Object Model to automate the Gallery Application.
Locators and the Elements definition are defined separately in different files for better readability.
To Run the script:
1. Install Node, Appium.
2. Use either intellij or eclipse.
3. Add selenium  java appium client, mockito, commons-io, commoms-lang2-2.11,hamcrest,guice jar's
4. If using an emulator, then please update the platformVersion and launch the emulator first. Make sure that the application is installed in the emulator.
5. Run the file 'execution.xml'

